        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". St. Luke does not say that five thousand of St. Peter’s hearers were converted, in addition to those already converted at Pentecost (although Dr. Hort, following Chrys., Aug[149], Jer[150], takes this view, ",
        "children": []
